{"title":"大地的深情","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地的深情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地滋养我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我一树浓荫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管岁月在我脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烙上一块块斑痕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻进年轮的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有历史的风风雨雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在风雨中成长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一片绿叶都在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诵赞太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十级台风也拧不断腰杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因我的根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧抓着大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风起时换一身黄金甲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪纷飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将全部落叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回赠大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我全身赤裸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但秃而不枯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老来又发新枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无以回报土地的深恩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有年复一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荫更浓，叶更绿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：南京《雨花》编辑部）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}